{"tid":1222362,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今日吹風話政府撤，依到有一定唔會撤既証據","createTime":"2019-06-14T11:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T12:10:05.000Z","uid":5809,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ec435d725d11f8ab83815985a44e922439147957","tid":1222362,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mWf8A1g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmWf8A1g.png&h=a0270081&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">你地信燒山定班保皇狗？</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人今鋪要靠自己，我地要打破命運，自己香港自己救！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就算阻擋係我地面前既係座山，我地都要破開佢！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今個星期日，再創奇蹟！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"4da68b655e1b0c1217efc0885c4d51bc5333e4dd","tid":1222362,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:59:19.000Z","msg":"同場加映<br />\n &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁多位香港人,大家認為星期日上街係為左咩!?<br />\n<br />\n為左抗惡法?無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗迫林鄭下台?無錯</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但最重要既係保護香港人!!!!!!!!!!</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時最少已經有11個香港人為咗我地被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當中包括為咗我地而食棍!!!中椒!!!同埋中槍既香港人!!!!!!<br />\n星期日上街我地一定要為佢地發聲!!!唔可以忘記佢地!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n大家集中目標:<br />\n1.撤回送中惡法<br />\n2.林鄭及相關官員必須問責下台<br />\n3.釋放所有被捕人士及保證不會檢控任何示威者<br />\n4.起訴涉嫌謀殺之警員及其上司<br />\n5.成立具效力之警方濫用暴力調查組織<br />\n6.釋放所有在囚政治人士,包括黃之鋒及梁天琦<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港人,記得一個都不能少!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n唔可以放棄任何一個自己人!!!!!!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"459042717f3578ed83a94d708dd7ff4236728126","tid":1222362,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c3a348fec932d843f80611df6f22ce749b8b2b","tid":1222362,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:00:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3366f04bb23b6d129f85007d87071f93e15a74f1","tid":1222362,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:00:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fd0ab1bbd7c87bc88e749a19c5d67cadbaf90af","tid":1222362,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:01:56.000Z","msg":"燒山又如何，我地要打破命運既詛咒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12d3b725cb5e5460e95504fee12f8fa82f4afab","tid":1222362,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:03:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a4efc3d6cce280b91cd9af960c649f2d500fa3b","tid":1222362,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:10:05.000Z","msg":"香港人，集氣，一次過戰勝共產黨同燒山<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}